paragraphs.text:
%sql
select
  genreName, sum(userTaggedCount) as totalTagged,
  count(genreBookId) as booksTagged
  from books_genres
  group by genreName
  having booksTagged > 1000
  order by totalTagged desc

order by ratingsCount desc
limit 100
